column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra,p.dec,p.petror9#_r, p.dered_g, s.z as z_spec, s.zErr, zns.t0#_smooth_or_features_a0#_smooth_fraction, zns.t0#_odd_feature_a2#_irregular_fraction, zns.t0#_odd_feature_a2#_merger_fraction   FROM Galaxy as p    JOIN zoo2MainSpecz AS zns ON p.specobjid = zns.specobjid    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE p.clean=#
